summary: An Ordinance accepting a deed from Charles P. H. Dose and Ida Dose, his wife, to a portion of Government Lot Two (2) in Section Ten (10), Township Twenty-four (24) North, Range Four (4) East Willamette Meridian, to the City of Seattle, executed on May 7, 1912, for the extensions of Dose Terrace and 34th Avenue South.
